            <div class="containerTitlesBig textCenter" style="color: #E6E6E6;">WELCOME TO HAZARDOUS ENVIRONMENTS</div>
        </div>

        <div id="day-selector">
            <a href="/hazardousenvironments">
                <div class="day-selector-day">DAY 1</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/hazardousenvironments/features">
                <div class="day-selector-day">DAY 2</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/hazardousenvironments/weapons">
                <div class="day-selector-day day-selector-day-selected">DAY 3</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/hazardousenvironments/release">
                <div class="day-selector-day">DAY 4</div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="containerBox textCenter">
            <div class="containerTitlesBig">INTRODUCING 4 NEW CUSTOM WEAPONS</div>
            <div class="containerDescriptions">You asked, we listened.<br>That's right, after a collectively long-time wait we're finally introducing 4 weapons that will be usable on every Creators.TF server. These weapons were tested to hell and
                made us feel we were losing our minds for some days.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="containerBox">
            <div class="weaponShowcase row align-items-center textRight">
                <div class="weaponShowcase-img">
                    <img src="{CDN}/assets/images/tf_pages/hazardousenvironments/weapons/weapon_allclass_crowbar.png">
                </div>
                <div class="weaponShowcase-info col-sm">
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorName">CRATE SMASHER</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">A near-perfect replica of a certain crowbar. If only you could climb through vents...</div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span>An all-class melee weapon</span>
                        <span>This weapon was made by: Loyen</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=152814592" target="_blank">
                        <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">
                            Vote for this item on the
                            <img src="/cdn/assets/images/steamworkshoplogo.png" style="width: 250px;">
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="containerBox">
            <div class="weaponShowcase row align-items-center">
                <div class="weaponShowcase-info col-sm">
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorName" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">GAMMA GAZER</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">Packs a mean dose of extra-hertz</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span>A secondary weapon for Engineer</span>
                        <span>This weapon was made by: Gadget and FiveEyes</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">Damage removes Sappers</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">+100% damage bonus</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">Requires 40 metal per shot to destroy the Sapper</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-350% slower firing speed</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-50% clip size</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-76% max secondary ammo on wearer</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=229535075" target="_blank">
                        <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">
                            Vote for this item on the
                            <img src="/cdn/assets/images/steamworkshoplogo.png" style="width: 250px;">
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="weaponShowcase-img">
                    <img src="{CDN}/assets/images/tf_pages/hazardousenvironments/weapons/weapon_engineer_gamma_gazer.png">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="containerBox">
            <div class="weaponShowcase row align-items-center textRight">
                <div class="weaponShowcase-img">
                    <img src="{CDN}/assets/images/tf_pages/hazardousenvironments/weapons/weapon_allclass_rapidfire.png">
                </div>
                <div class="weaponShowcase-info col-sm">
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorName" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">THE THUMPER</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">A near perfect replica of the classic scientific shotgun</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span>A primary/secondary weapon for Soldier, Pyro, Heavy and Engineer</span>
                        <span>This weapon was made by: Sparkwire and Svdl</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">+130% damage bonus</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">+30% clip size</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">+50% max ammo</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">15% more accurate</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-20% slower firing speed</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-50% bullets per shot</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">13% slower reload time</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">This weapon deploys 15% slower</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=731" target="_blank">
                        <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">
                            Vote for this item on the
                            <img src="/cdn/assets/images/steamworkshoplogo.png" style="width: 250px;">
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="containerBox">
            <div class="weaponShowcase row align-items-center">
                <div class="weaponShowcase-info col-sm">
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-colorName">THE HYPODERMIC INJECTOR</div>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">Hold still, this will only sting for a moment</div>
                        <span>A syringe weapon for Medic (literally)</span>
                        <span>This weapon was made by: Zoey</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="weaponShowcase-atributes">
                        <span>Collect blood from your enemies by hurting them and heal your teammates by transferring blood to them.</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">Can store up to 300 health points</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">Heal your teammates by hitting them with this weapon</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-goodSide">+10% faster firing speed</span>
                        <span class="weaponShowcase-badSide">-20% damage penalty</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=433097312" target="_blank">
                        <div class="weaponShowcase-colorDescription">
                            Vote for this item on the
                            <img src="/cdn/assets/images/steamworkshoplogo.png" style="width: 250px;">
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="weaponShowcase-img">
                    <img src="{CDN}/assets/images/tf_pages/hazardousenvironments/weapons/item_weapon_hypodemic_injector.png">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

